  ],
  "remarks": "Vitaly Kuzmenko is the General Director of JSC 163 Armor Repair Plant. JSC 163 Armor Repair Plant’s primary activity is maintenance of T-72 main battle tanks and BMP-2 amphibious infantry fighting vehicles. The plant is part of the High Precision Systems holding company of Rostec. Various models of BMP-2 infantry fighting vehicles and T-72 main battle tanks are used by the Russian army in the war of aggression against Ukraine. JSC 163 Armor Repair Plant set a record in the maintenance of BMP-2 in 2023.",
